headline: Arthur J. Gallagher & Co. Acquires Hunt Financial Group
summary: Arthur J. Gallagher & Co. today announced the acquisition of Hunt Benefits & Associates, Inc., and Tenaglia & Associates, Inc., collectively dba Hunt Financial Group. Terms of the transaction were not disclosed.

headline: Arthur J. Gallagher & Co. Acquires Reck & Co.
summary: Arthur J. Gallagher & Co. today announced that its claims and risk management solutions subsidiary, Gallagher Bassett, has acquired Bremen, Germany-based Reck & Co GmbH ("Reck & Co."). Terms of the transaction were not disclosed.
